    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="a-frame-work-for-variation-discovery-and-genotyping-using-next-genetation-dna-sequencing-data">A frame work for variation discovery and genotyping using next-genetation DNA sequencing data</h3>
<p><em>Mark A DePristo .etc</em></p>

<h4 id="abstract">Abstract</h4>
<p>A frame work to discovery and genotype variation among multiple samples <br />
across five sequencing technologies and three canonical experimental design.</p>

<p>process:</p>

<ul>
  <li>initial read mapping</li>
  <li>local alignment around indels</li>
  <li>base quality score recalibration</li>
  <li>SNP discovery and genotyping to find all potential variants</li>
  <li>machine learing to separate true segreating variation from machnie artifacts
common to next-generation sequencing tech.</li>
</ul>

